# SPECIALIZE — Futamura projection engine as a super/ op
#
# Exposes the partial evaluator to the MAP runtime via Python hooks.
# Once this op is registered, you can call from any MAP program:
#
#   {PE-SPECIALIZE expr senv-alist}    → residual expression
#   {FUTAMURA-1 program-expr}          → compiled program (as expression)
#   {FUTAMURA-2}                       → compiler description
#   {FUTAMURA-3}                       → compiler-compiler description
#   {PE-FOLD expr}                     → fully reduce if all-static, else residual
#
# The hot-reload engine means you can {self-rewrite SPECIALIZE new-source}
# to evolve the partial evaluator while it's running — the 3rd projection
# made literal.

{print :OP :SPECIALIZE :LOADED}
{print :FUTAMURA :PROJECTIONS :READY}
